      <h2>Equipments</h2>
      <h3>Compute Infrastructure</h3>
      <p>VUB-ETRO is equipped with a extensive compute infrastructure spanning multiple tiers. The lab has dedicated high-end NVIDIA GPUs at the desktop level for interactive coding and testing, a local GPU cluster (Tier-3) for on-demand computing with state-of-the-art accelerators, and priority access to VUB's Tier-2 infrastructure featuring latest-generation NVIDIA A100 and H200 nodes. Additionally, researchers can access the Flemish Tier-1 supercomputing resources (VSC), as well as VUB's newest Tier-1 system (Sofia) — a major investment operational since 2025.</p>

